ining space.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/22102309\/beige-tile-epoxy-floor-design.jpg\" alt=\"Beige tile finish epoxy floor design idea for a modular dining room for an elegant look\" class=\"wp-image-55840\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/22102309\/beige-tile-epoxy-floor-design.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/22102309\/beige-tile-epoxy-floor-design-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/22102309\/beige-tile-epoxy-floor-design-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/22102309\/beige-tile-epoxy-floor-design-50x30.jpg 50w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/22102309\/beige-tile-epoxy-floor-design-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">An elegant dining room<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Beach-like 3D Epoxy Flooring for an Inviting Patio<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Create a coastal oasis in your backyard with a beach-like epoxy floor featuring a coarse sandy texture. Adorned with outdoor-worthy wicker sofas, wall sconces, a barbecue machine, and lush greenery, this patio will become an inviting retreat for every guest.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/22102256\/3d-epoxy-floor-design.jpg\" alt=\"3-D epoxy floor design idea for patio, which gives the beach-like vibe\" class=\"wp-image-55839\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/22102256\/3d-epoxy-floor-design.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/22102256\/3d-epoxy-floor-design-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/22102256\/3d-epoxy-floor-design-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/22102256\/3d-epoxy-floor-design-50x30.jpg 50w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/22102256\/3d-epoxy-floor-design-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Hyper-realistic 3D epoxy flooring glams up the home<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Faux Marble Epoxy Floor for Spacious Island Kitchen<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Unleash your inner chef in a spacious <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/guides\/everything-know-about-kitchen-islands\/\">island kitchen<\/a> boasting a faux marble epoxy floor with captivating black and white swirls. Complemented by various modern modular cabinetry like a hidden vertical bar cabinet, this design stunningly blends sophistication with functionality.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/22102243\/faux-marble-epoxy-floor-design.jpg\" alt=\"Faux marble epoxy floor design idea for the spacious island kitchen\" class=\"wp-image-55838\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/22102243\/faux-marble-epoxy-floor-design.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/22102243\/faux-marble-epoxy-floor-design-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/22102243\/faux-marble-epoxy-floor-design-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/22102243\/faux-marble-epoxy-floor-design-50x30.jpg 50w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/22102243\/faux-marble-epoxy-floor-design-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Make your kitchen look like a million bucks!<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Revive your home with modern and affordable home interiors!\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/09144537\/revive-your-home-with-modern-and-affordable-home-interiors.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Neoclassical Entryway with Chequered Epoxy Flooring\u00a0<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Make a grand entrance in this neoclassical-style entryway featuring a chequered epoxy floor. Paired with modern <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-interiors\/types-of-modular-furniture\/\">modular furniture<\/a>, this entryway hits the right balance between timeless charm and modern amenities, setting the stage for a warm welcome.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/22102230\/chequered-epoxy-floor-design.jpg\" alt=\"Chequered epoxy floor design idea for a neoclassical entryway\" class=\"wp-image-55837\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/22102230\/chequered-epoxy-floor-design.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/22102230\/chequered-epoxy-floor-design-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/22102230\/chequered-epoxy-floor-design-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/22102230\/chequered-epoxy-floor-design-50x30.jpg 50w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/22102230\/chequered-epoxy-floor-design-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Achieve an illusion of depth with 3D chequered epoxy floors<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>In a nutshell, epoxy flooring opens up a world of design possibilities, allowing you to transform your space into a work of art. They are a great way to add style and durability to your home. The showcased designs are just a glimpse of what epoxy floors can achieve. If you are inspired and ready to elevate your space with these stunning designs, <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/contact-us\/\">book a free consultation<\/a> with our in-house interior designers and explore more design inspiration in our <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/\">blog section<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">FAQs On Epoxy Flooring Designs<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Are there any safety concerns with using epoxy flooring?<\/strong><br>Epoxy flooring is generally considered safe. However, exposure to high amounts of epoxy fumes during the curing process may cause sensitization and asthma. Therefore, it is better to appoint professionals to install epoxy flooring.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>What is the cost of installing epoxy floors?<\/strong><br>The cost of installing epoxy floors varies depending on the size of the area being covered, the type of epoxy being used, and the complexity of the design. However, in India, epoxy flooring installation costs between \u20b930-\u20b9150\/sq. ft.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Can epoxy flooring be used in areas with moisture or water exposure?<\/strong><br>Yes, epoxy flooring can be used in areas with moisture or water exposure. However, it is important to use a high-quality epoxy product specifically designed for wet areas. It is also important to apply anti-skid material over your epoxy flooring in wet areas, as it tends to get very slippery.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>What is the average lifespan of epoxy flooring?<\/strong><br>The average lifespan of epoxy flooring is 10-15 years. However, with proper care and maintenance, epoxy flooring can last many years.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"row blog-form\">\n\t<div class=\"offset-lg-3 col-lg-6 bg-light